com.lucidworks.fusion.connector.plugin.api.plugin

Class ConnectorPluginModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pf4j.Plugin
      • com.lucidworks.fusion.plugin.PluginModule
        • com.lucidworks.fusion.connector.plugin.api.plugin.ConnectorPluginModule

  • public abstract class ConnectorPluginModule
extends com.lucidworks.fusion.plugin.PluginModule
    All connector plugins extend this class. The main function of this class is to provide a base class method that can get the Connector.

    This class overrides "start()" such that when a plugin is started, it will start the GrpcConnectorPluginClient which will establish the bi-directional communication between this Plugin and the GrpcServer's API Service.
